 Today we are going to make a rainbow loom band cake, with rainbow glaze between the layers 

00:00:08.069 --> 00:00:13.530
 and a huge loom band bracelet on the top. For the uninitiated: loom band are small 

00:00:13.530 --> 00:00:18.289
 strap that you weave together to make a bracelet and all other creations. 

00:00:18.289 --> 00:00:24.159
 First you need two quantities of the sponge cake recipe and two quantities 

00:00:24.159 --> 00:00:28.749
 make recipes from one of the frosting. The sponge cake and frosting recipes and all videos 

00:00:28.749 --> 00:00:33.520
 how to make them are all on the website '' howtocookthat.net '' and I will provide a link 

00:00:33.520 --> 00:00:38.910
 in the description below the video. Put 2/3 cup of your glaze in 5 different containers 

00:00:38.910 --> 00:00:44.140
 and mix your pink color in the first. I use the French here 

00:00:44.140 --> 00:00:48.710
 buttercream glaze recipe you can use all the recipes that I have on the website 

00:00:48.710 --> 00:00:53.920
 use the one that you like best. I make all pastel colors, 

00:00:53.920 --> 00:00:59.030
 if you want them brighter, you can of course add more dye. After that I have 

00:00:59.030 --> 00:01:02.810
 orange, yellow, green and blue mixed. 

00:01:02.810 --> 00:01:08.729
 Use a cake leveler or a knife to cut your sponge cakes in half and remove the top 

00:01:08.729 --> 00:01:10.929
 from one off. 

00:01:10.929 --> 00:01:15.189
 Place your first glance on your cake stand and spread the pink glaze over the top, 

00:01:15.189 --> 00:01:20.869
 close to, but not all the way to the edges so that when you place the next layer on it 

00:01:20.869 --> 00:01:26.210
 do not spray everything from the edges. Continue stacking with the other colors. 

00:01:26.210 --> 00:01:30.709
 A few weeks ago I made youtube cupcakes with all your favorite youtubers on it 

00:01:30.709 --> 00:01:34.009
 and some asked if I could do something like that with apps. And I thought that is 

